main event: A bright flash of white light was observed over NAS Key West, Florida on December 3, 1956.
interesting points: The sighting lasted only a few seconds,The observer could not determine the size or distance of the object, The observation was made from the control tower at NAS Key West, The azimuth of the object was 90 degrees from Key West NAS, Various potential explanations were considered including a balloon and aircraft.
sighted object: a bright flash of white light
witness description: civilian observer from NAS Key West control tower
